node.text: The Grand Theft Auto series has skyrocketed to the top of video game sales since the first game came on the scene in 1997, despite its many public controversies. Find out how the game has become one of the most profitable entertainment franchises of all time.

node.text: @fujiwarahiroshi and @MSI have joined forces on the new Creator Z16 Hiroshi Fujiwara Limited Edition laptop. The notebook is built to cater to the needs of modern day multi-hyphenate creatives, and Fujiwara lends his unmissable aesthetic to its exterior with graphics inspired by the golden ratio of the special edition’s 16:10 monitor. Especially the mini LED display will astonish creators’ visual experience.  #sponsored

#hypeAF: @pokemon Center has released Snorlax and Ditto bean bag chairs made by @yogibobags as part of its Pokémon Home Accents collection. The first generation Pokémon bean bags measure 7.5-pound/45 by 40-inch and 10-pound/45 by 30-inch bean bags respectively, each retailing for $200 USD. You can purchase them now via the Pokémon Center website.⁠
Photo: Pokémon Center

node.text:
@hypebeastcarclub: German luxury RV specialist @volkner.mobil has released its most expensive motor home to date. The Volkner Performance S sees an L-shaped kitchen, a master suite, a full-width bathroom, a 2,000-watt solar array, a wine locker, and a Burmester sound system that costs $355,000 USD alone. Adding to the $7.7 million price tag is a @bugatti Chiron stowed in a slide-out garage. Get a closer look via the link in bio.⁠
Photo: Volkner

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by HYPEBEAST on September 07, 2021 tagging @netflix. May be a cartoon of 1 person and text that says 'HYPEBEAST NETFLIX'S NEW 'BAKI HANMA' TRAILER WELCOMES THE ULTIMATE FATHER-SON BRAWL'.

node.text:
In case you missed it, @netflix recently unveiled the second official trailer for ‘Baki Hanma,’ the third installment of the anime series based on the highly-acclaimed manga ‘Baki’ by Keisuke Itagaki. The clip sees Baki challenge his father Yujiro, commonly referred to as “the strongest creature on Earth,” after the Great Raitai Tournament Saga, making way for a brutal father-son face-off. Watch it now via the link in bio.⁠
Photo: Netflix

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by HYPEBEAST on September 07, 2021 tagging @cassia.global. May be an image of skyscraper.

node.text:
#hypeAF: @cassia.global has unveiled its project for Africa’s second tallest building. Located in Zanzibar, the structure is inspired by dominoes and is set to be 70 stories tall. Amenities include 560 residential units, a five and six-star hotel, spas, green walls, four helipads, 104 over-water villas, an arrival dock, a three-par golf course, and F&B outdoor areas that can accommodate up to 800 guests. Find out more via the link in bio.⁠
Photo: xCassia

node.text:
@hypefoods: Premium Bandai has released ‘JUJUTSU KAISEN’-inspired items, including a chocolate mold to mimic the antagonist Ryomen Sukuna’s fingers. Each mold can make five fingers at a time which can be topped off with toasted almonds as fingernails for a more realistic look. Find it now on Premium Bandai’s website for approximately $34 USD and tag a friend who’d want this.⁠
Photo: Premium Bandai
